hudson.tasks.Shell.command:
export NVM_DIR="$HOME/.nvm" curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash [ -s "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" ] && \. "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" [ -s "$NVM_DIR/bash_completion" ] && \. "$NVM_DIR/bash_completion" nvm install 20.12.2 nvm use 20.12.2
export PATH="$PATH:$HOME/.nvm/versions/node/`nvm current`/bin"
node --version npm -version
ls -la cd .. ls -la node --version cd .. ls -la node --version cd .. ls -la node --version cd .. ls -la node --version cd autotest ls -la node --version npm -version npm install npm run wdio:docker
